  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataPersistence
    Implementation of XStream for persisting user data.
    Infraction
    Object which stores an instance of an infraction committed by a Player.
    LeagueAnalysis
    Static class which stores the lists of Team and Match in the league, and performs operations on them.
    LocalDateTimeConverter
    Converts LocalDateTime objects for more readable storage
    Match
    Object representing an instance of a match, and all its relevant information.
    Player
    Object representing a single player, and all their relevant fields.
    PlayerAnalysis
    Static Object which stores and controls information pertaining to all the players in the league.
    ShotOnGoal
    Object which stores the instance of an attempted shot on a goal.
    Team
    Object which stores all information related to a single team.
